Package: histogramplot
Title: Make histogram plots for a certain variable in different groups
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Grace",
           family = "Yin",
           email = "zhugeliangspurs@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package is used for data visualization, especially when there is
    a group variable in a dataset.It contains the function histogram_plot
    that can make histogram plots for a certain variable 
    in different groups or levels in the dataset seperately.
